summary: In my latest CR dream, the Mighty Nein all attended some sort of dance, and I was Nott (or at least cosplaying Nott?), and I...
body: In my latest CR dream, the Mighty Nein all attended some sort of dance, and I was Nott (or at least cosplaying Nott?), and I went up to Caduceus, who was hovering awkwardly on the sidelines, and tried to convince him that Caleb wanted to dance with him. (Caleb had expressed no such desire.) This is such a Nott-the-interfering-mom thing to do that I’m still laughing about it.

blog.name: kacka07
blog.title: There is freedom in the dark.
blog.description:
KATE / 22 / CZECH
-
"Odysseus, on his journey home to Ithaca, is visited by a ghost. The ghost tells him that once he reaches his home — once he slays all his enemies and sets his house in order — he must do one last thing before he can rest. The ghost tells him to pick up an oar and walk inland, and keep walking until somebody mistakes that oar for a shovel. For that would be a place where no man had ever been troubled by the sea, and that's where he'd find peace."
